        <div class="process-section">
            <div class="process-card">
                <h3>üìê Design Process & Iterations</h3>
                <p>The visualization evolved through three key iterations:</p>
                <div class="sketch-container">
                    <div class="sketch">
                        <h4>Iteration 1: Radial Cluster Map</h4>
                        <div style="width:100%;height:150px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e40af,#1d4ed8);border-radius:8px;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;color:white;font-weight:bold;">
                            Radial Layout
                        </div>
                        <p>Traditional circular layout with guest segments in rings</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sketch">
                        <h4>Iteration 2: Temporal Flow River</h4>
                        <div style="width:100%;height:150px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7c3aed,#a78bfa);border-radius:8px;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;color:white;font-weight:bold;">
                            Flow Diagram
                        </div>
                        <p>Timeline-based flow showing guest journey through hotel stay</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sketch">
                        <h4>Iteration 3: Behavioral Terrain Map</h4>
                        <div style="width:100%;height:150px;background:linear-gradient(45deg,#0d9488,#14b8a6);border-radius:8px;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;color:white;font-weight:bold;">
                            3D Terrain
                        </div>
                        <p>Topographical map with peaks representing high-value segments</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sketch">
                        <h4>Final: Guest Constellation</h4>
                        <div style="width:100%;height:150px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b,#0f172a);border-radius:8px;display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;color:#60a5fa;font-weight:bold;border:2px solid #60a5fa;">
                            ‚òÖ Constellation ‚òÖ
                        </div>
                        <p>Celestial metaphor with guests as stars in behavioral space</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="process-card">
                <h3>üé® Design Principles & Rule-Breaking</h3>
                <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <h4 style="color:#10b981;margin-bottom:10px;">Traditional Rules We Bent:</h4>
                    <ul style="padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.8;">
                        <li><strong>Color Semantics:</strong> Used color for aesthetic harmony rather than categorical distinction</li>
                        <li><strong>Data-Ink Ratio:</strong> Embraced decorative elements (glows, animations) over minimalism</li>
                        <li><strong>Immediate Readability:</strong> Prioritized exploration over instant comprehension</li>
                        <li><strong>2D Representation:</strong> Created pseudo-3D space through layering and glow effects</li>
                    </ul>
                    
                    <h4 style="color:#f59e0b;margin-bottom:10px;">Novel Color Usage:</h4>
                    <p>Colors represent <strong>emotional resonance</strong> rather than data categories:</p>
                    <ul style="padding-left:20px;line-height:1.8;">
                        <li><span style="color:#60a5fa">‚óè Blue:</span> Calm, business-like efficiency</li>
                        <li><span style="color:#10b981">‚óè Green:</span> Family-friendly, nurturing</li>
                        <li><span style="color:#f59e0b">‚óè Yellow:</span> Romantic, warm experiences</li>
                        <li><span style="color:#ec4899">‚óè Pink:</span> Spontaneous, impulsive decisions</li>
                        <li><span style="color:#8b5cf6">‚óè Purple:</span> Loyalty, premium experiences</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="reflection">
            <h3>üîÆ Reflection & Intent</h3>
            <div class="reflection-grid">
                <div class="reflection-item">
                    <h4>What We Aimed For</h4>
                    <p>To create an <strong>emotional connection</strong> with hotel guest data, transforming dry statistics into a captivating cosmic narrative. We wanted managers to feel they're exploring a universe of guest possibilities rather than analyzing spreadsheets.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="reflection-item">
                    <h4>Design Rules We Broke</h4>
                    <p>We intentionally violated Tufte's data-ink ratio principle, embracing decorative elements to create visual delight. We used <strong>non-semantic color coding</strong> and prioritized aesthetic harmony over immediate data readability, asking viewers to explore rather than simply consume.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="reflection-item">
                    <h4>Intended Audience</h4>
                    <p>Hotel <strong>marketing teams</strong> and <strong>executive leadership</strong> who need to develop an intuitive, emotional understanding of their guest segments for strategic planning and brand development, not just operational optimization.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="reflection-item">
                    <h4>Data Attributes Encoded</h4>
                    <p><strong>‚úì 7 Attributes Total:</strong><br>
                    1. Guest Segment (Star Position)<br>
                    2. Revenue Potential (Star Size)<br>
                    3. Cancellation Risk (Star Pulse Speed)<br>
                    4. Service Requirements (Connection Lines)<br>
                    5. Booking Lead Time (Orbital Distance)<br>
                    6. Stay Duration (Ring Count)<br>
                    7. Special Requests (Aura Effect)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Tooltip for star details -->
    <div class="tooltip" id="starTooltip"></div>
    
    <script>
        // Generate the constellation visualization
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const container = document.getElementById('constellation');
            const tooltip = document.getElementById('starTooltip');
            
            // Guest segment data - each represents a different guest type
            const guestSegments = [
                { name: "Corporate Executive", type: "business", x: 30, y: 40, size: 28, 
                  revenue: 850, cancellation: 0.15, leadTime: 7, stayDuration: 2, requests: 3 },
                { name: "Weekend Family", type: "family", x: 70, y: 25, size: 32, 
                  revenue: 1200, cancellation: 0.08, leadTime: 14, stayDuration: 4, requests: 5 },
                { name: "Honeymoon Couple", type: "romantic", x: 50, y: 70, size: 24, 
                  revenue: 1800, cancellation: 0.03, leadTime: 90, stayDuration: 7, requests: 8 },
                { name: "Last-Minute Booker", type: "lastMinute", x: 20, y: 75, size: 20, 
                  revenue: 650, cancellation: 0.35, leadTime: 1, stayDuration: 2, requests: 1 },
                { name: "Loyalty Platinum", type: "loyalty", x: 80, y: 60, size: 35, 
                  revenue: 1500, cancellation: 0.05, leadTime: 21, stayDuration: 5, requests: 4 },
                { name: "Conference Attendee", type: "business", x: 40, y: 20, size: 26, 
                  revenue: 950, cancellation: 0.12, leadTime: 30, stayDuration: 3, requests: 2 },
                { name: "Extended Family", type: "family", x: 75, y: 80, size: 30, 
                  revenue: 2200, cancellation: 0.10, leadTime: 60, stayDuration: 10, requests: 7 },
                { name: "Anniversary Couple", type: "romantic", x: 25, y: 55, size: 22, 
                  revenue: 1600, cancellation: 0.04, leadTime: 45, stayDuration: 4, requests: 6 },
                { name: "Spontaneous Getaway", type: "lastMinute", x: 65, y: 40, size: 18, 
                  revenue: 550, cancellation: 0.40, leadTime: 2, stayDuration: 2, requests: 1 },
                { name: "Loyalty Gold", type: "loyalty", x: 55, y: 35, size: 27, 
                  revenue: 1100, cancellation: 0.08, leadTime: 14, stayDuration: 4, requests: 3 }
            ];
            
            // Color mapping for guest types
            const typeColors = {
                business: "#60a5fa",
                family: "#10b981",
                romantic: "#f59e0b",
                lastMinute: "#ec4899",
                loyalty: "#8b5cf6"
            };
            
            // Create stars
            guestSegments.forEach(guest => {
                const star = document.createElement('div');
                star.className = 'star';
                
                // Calculate position percentages
                const left = guest.x;
                const top = guest.y;
                
                // Size based on revenue
                const size = guest.size;
                
                // Color based on type
                const color = typeColors[guest.type];
                
                // Apply styles
                star.style.left = `${left}%`;
                star.style.top = `${top}%`;
                star.style.width = `${size}px`;
                star.style.height = `${size}px`;
                star.style.backgroundColor = color;
                star.style.color = color;
                
                // Create rings around star for stay duration
                for (let i = 1; i <= guest.stayDuration; i++) {
                    const ring = document.createElement('div');
                    ring.style.position = 'absolute';
                    ring.style.left = '50%';
                    ring.style.top = '50%';
                    ring.style.width = `${size + (i * 15)}px`;
                    ring.style.height = `${size + (i * 15)}px`;
                    ring.style.border = `1px solid ${color}`;
                    ring.style.borderRadius = '50%';
                    ring.style.transform = 'translate(-50%, -50%)';
                    ring.style.opacity = 0.2 - (i * 0.03);
                    star.appendChild(ring);
                }
                
                // Add pulse animation speed based on cancellation risk
                const pulseSpeed = 2 + (guest.cancellation * 10);
                star.style.animationDuration = `${pulseSpeed}s`;
                
                // Add hover event for tooltip
                star.addEventListener('mouseenter', function(e) {
                    // Show tooltip
                    tooltip.style.opacity = '1';
                    tooltip.style.left = `${e.pageX + 15}px`;
                    tooltip.style.top = `${e.pageY + 15}px`;
                    
                    // Populate tooltip content
                    tooltip.innerHTML = `
                        <div class="tooltip-header">${guest.name}</div>
                        <div class="tooltip-row">
                            <span class="attribute">Revenue Potential:</span>
                            <span class="value">$${guest.revenue}/stay</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tooltip-row">
                            <span class="attribute">Cancellation Risk:</span>
                            <span class="value">${(guest.cancellation * 100).toFixed(0)}%</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tooltip-row">
                            <span class="attribute">Avg Lead Time:</span>
                            <span class="value">${guest.leadTime} days</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tooltip-row">
                            <span class="attribute">Stay Duration:</span>
                            <span class="value">${guest.stayDuration} nights</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tooltip-row">
                            <span class="attribute">Special Requests:</span>
                            <span class="value">${guest.requests} avg</span>
                        </div>
                    `;
                });
                
                star.addEventListener('mousemove', function(e) {
                    tooltip.style.left = `${e.pageX + 15}px`;
                    tooltip.style.top = `${e.pageY + 15}px`;
                });
                
                star.addEventListener('mouseleave', function() {
                    tooltip.style.opacity = '0';
                });
                
                container.appendChild(star);
            });
            
            // Create connections between related segments
            const connections = [
                { from: 0, to: 5 }, // Business to Conference
                { from: 1, to: 6 }, // Family to Extended Family
                { from: 2, to: 7 }, // Romantic to Anniversary
                { from: 3, to: 8 }, // Last-minute to Spontaneous
                { from: 4, to: 9 }, // Loyalty tiers
                { from: 0, to: 9 }, // Business to Loyalty
                { from: 2, to: 4 }, // Romantic to Loyalty
                { from: 1, to: 9 }, // Family to Loyalty
            ];
            
            connections.forEach(conn => {
                const fromGuest = guestSegments[conn.from];
                const toGuest = guestSegments[conn.to];
                
                const connection = document.createElement('div');
                connection.className = 'connection';
                
                // Calculate line position and angle
                const x1 = fromGuest.x;
                const y1 = fromGuest.y;
                const x2 = toGuest.x;
                const y2 = toGuest.y;
                
                const length = Math.sqrt(Math.pow(x2 - x1, 2) + Math.pow(y2 - y1, 2));
                const angle = Math.atan2(y2 - y1, x2 - x1) * 180 / Math.PI;
                
                // Position at first point
                connection.style.left = `${x1}%`;
                connection.style.top = `${y1}%`;
                connection.style.width = `${length}%`;
                connection.style.transform = `rotate(${angle}deg)`;
                
                // Color based on types
                const fromColor = typeColors[fromGuest.type];
                const toColor = typeColors[toGuest.type];
                
                // Create gradient for connection
                connection.style.background = `linear-gradient(to right, ${fromColor}, ${toColor})`;
                
                container.appendChild(connection);
            });
            
            // Add some random smaller stars for background effect
            for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
                const bgStar = document.createElement('div');
                bgStar.style.position = 'absolute';
                bgStar.style.left = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
                bgStar.style.top = `${Math.random() * 100}%`;
                bgStar.style.width = `${Math.random() * 5 + 2}px`;
                bgStar.style.height = bgStar.style.width;
                bgStar.style.backgroundColor = '#e2e8f0';
                bgStar.style.borderRadius = '50%';
                bgStar.style.opacity = Math.random() * 0.5 + 0.2;
                bgStar.style.boxShadow = '0 0 4px white';
                container.appendChild(bgStar);
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
